docs.text: About mkdocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site called ./site . mkdocs gh-deploy push your document site to github pages mkdocs help - Print this help message. Tips: Add echo "site/" >> .gitignore to .gitignore file Project layout 1 2 3 4 5 mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. theme:... Theme pip install mkdocs-material and Add it to mkdocs.yml.
